379
00:26:41,940 --> 00:26:43,860
[Yanming Palace]

380
00:27:03,980 --> 00:27:04,780
Thank you, Father.

381
00:27:10,330 --> 00:27:11,130
Jinghe,

382
00:27:12,370 --> 00:27:14,460
I've sent you to Jingbei for ten years.

383
00:27:15,650 --> 00:27:16,980
Do you harbor any resentment?

384
00:27:27,810 --> 00:27:28,570
Father.

385
00:27:29,570 --> 00:27:31,540
In the past, I was too eager
for quick success

386
00:27:31,810 --> 00:27:33,090
and committed grave errors,

387
00:27:33,410 --> 00:27:35,940
failing to live up
to your earnest care and protection.

388
00:27:36,090 --> 00:27:37,570
You volunteered to escort
the marriage delegation.

389
00:27:38,170 --> 00:27:39,700
I thought you had come to your senses.

390
00:27:41,460 --> 00:27:43,370
But you scattered paper money
during the wedding procession in Jingbei.

391
00:27:43,610 --> 00:27:45,570
Could it be that you harbored
private resentment

392
00:27:46,170 --> 00:27:47,460
and intended to sabotage
the marriage alliance?

393
00:27:49,740 --> 00:27:50,700
Father,

394
00:27:51,700 --> 00:27:53,980
if I truly intended to sabotage
the marriage alliance,

395
00:27:53,980 --> 00:27:55,810
there would be plenty
of covert means to do so.

396
00:27:56,410 --> 00:27:58,060
Why would I make
such a public spectacle,

397
00:27:58,130 --> 00:27:59,740
giving the censors ammunition

398
00:27:59,980 --> 00:28:01,130
to file complaints against me?

399
00:28:01,330 --> 00:28:02,410
Then you were venting
personal resentment.

400
00:28:02,940 --> 00:28:03,460
I

401
00:28:03,890 --> 00:28:05,890
wouldn't dare disrupt your grand plans.

402
00:28:07,850 --> 00:28:08,700
Over these years

403
00:28:09,020 --> 00:28:10,940
of dealing with Xiyan,
I have come to understand

404
00:28:11,570 --> 00:28:14,220
that their king
is extremely patient and cunning.

405
00:28:14,740 --> 00:28:16,980
How do we know they aren't using
the marriage alliance

406
00:28:16,980 --> 00:28:18,060
as a chance to recuperate

407
00:28:18,300 --> 00:28:19,170
and regroup?

408
00:28:19,890 --> 00:28:21,740
Therefore, in my view,

409
00:28:22,130 --> 00:28:23,330
we must make a public example of them,

410
00:28:24,130 --> 00:28:25,500
so that Xiyan understands that agreeing

411
00:28:25,850 --> 00:28:26,850
to the marriage alliance

412
00:28:27,260 --> 00:28:29,300
is a great favor we are granting them.

413
00:28:29,700 --> 00:28:31,020
If they dare cause trouble again,

414
00:28:31,300 --> 00:28:32,220
there will be no leniency.

415
00:28:33,850 --> 00:28:35,300
I'm very happy that you understand

416
00:28:36,220 --> 00:28:37,060
all this.

417
00:28:39,610 --> 00:28:41,940
Don't make things difficult
for Xiyan people,

418
00:28:42,260 --> 00:28:43,500
especially Princess Zigu.

419
00:28:44,410 --> 00:28:46,700
Her brother is still a hostage
in Great Yan.

420
00:28:47,090 --> 00:28:49,170
Do not let this create a rift
between our countries.

421
00:28:49,890 --> 00:28:50,940
Otherwise, the marriage alliance

422
00:28:51,500 --> 00:28:52,610
will be meaningless.

423
00:28:53,650 --> 00:28:54,130
Yes.

424
00:28:54,700 --> 00:28:56,610
I will follow your instructions.

425
00:28:57,570 --> 00:28:58,130
Jinghe,

426
00:28:58,890 --> 00:29:00,060
allowing you to return to the capital

427
00:29:00,610 --> 00:29:02,370
has already invited criticism.

428
00:29:02,810 --> 00:29:04,460
The nursery rhyme
reflects public opinion.

429
00:29:04,940 --> 00:29:06,170
The public opinion is like water.

430
00:29:06,170 --> 00:29:08,610
Water can carry a boat,
but it can also capsize it.

431
00:29:11,890 --> 00:29:12,890
I understand.

432
00:29:18,540 --> 00:29:19,780
In the 14th year of the Zhaoming era,

433
00:29:21,700 --> 00:29:23,330
you volunteered to reclaim Qingzhou.

434
00:29:24,020 --> 00:29:25,570
You suffered in Qingzhou

435
00:29:25,940 --> 00:29:28,090
and was unable to see your mother
for the last time.

436
00:29:28,220 --> 00:29:30,170
I know that you harbor regret
and resentment

437
00:29:30,170 --> 00:29:31,170
in your heart.

438
00:29:31,540 --> 00:29:31,890
Father...

439
00:29:31,890 --> 00:29:32,410
Jinghe,

440
00:29:34,130 --> 00:29:35,130
your return to the capital this time

441
00:29:36,060 --> 00:29:37,650
is still about the old matters
of Qingzhou, right?

442
00:29:40,810 --> 00:29:41,330
Father,

443
00:29:42,300 --> 00:29:43,130
I wouldn't dare.

444
00:29:44,330 --> 00:29:45,020
Father, you've said

445
00:29:46,460 --> 00:29:47,570
that the events of Qingzhou

446
00:29:48,570 --> 00:29:49,650
should never be spoken of again.

447
00:29:54,300 --> 00:29:57,220
[Court of State Ceremonial]

448
00:29:59,300 --> 00:29:59,940
Look.

449
00:29:59,980 --> 00:30:01,300
Zhaojing is so prosperous.

450
00:30:01,540 --> 00:30:02,090
So beautiful.

451
00:30:02,090 --> 00:30:03,500
I've never seen these plants in Xiyan.

452
00:30:04,650 --> 00:30:05,650
I just saw someone

453
00:30:05,650 --> 00:30:06,890
selling Whitening Pills
at the street corner.

454
00:30:13,300 --> 00:30:16,540
When entering the city yesterday,
Your Highness must be frightened.

455
00:30:16,540 --> 00:30:18,370
Upon hearing of this, His Majesty

456
00:30:18,370 --> 00:30:22,220
has ordered Imperial Healer Zhang
to prepare a soothing potion for you.

457
00:30:23,850 --> 00:30:24,650
Well...

458
00:30:24,940 --> 00:30:27,700
Do I have to meet His Majesty
in the palace at once?

459
00:30:30,370 --> 00:30:33,260
Today is the late Empress'
death anniversary.

460
00:30:33,700 --> 00:30:36,610
I'm afraid His Majesty will have no time
to meet Your Highness.

461
00:30:37,020 --> 00:30:40,060
Besides, according to the customs
of Great Yan,

462
00:30:40,060 --> 00:30:42,460
joyous and mourning events
should not coincide.

463
00:30:43,260 --> 00:30:46,300
His Majesty specifically instructed me.

464
00:30:46,570 --> 00:30:48,460
Please forgive us.

465
00:30:49,940 --> 00:30:52,130
Given that Your Highness endured
a long and tiring journey,

466
00:30:52,130 --> 00:30:54,260
please first rest
at the Court of State Ceremonial

467
00:30:54,460 --> 00:30:58,700
and only enter the palace to meet
His Majesty during the alliance banquet.

468
00:31:07,890 --> 00:31:10,330
Mr. Yue Qin is also staying
in the Court of State Ceremonial,

469
00:31:10,330 --> 00:31:12,260
not far away from your place.

470
00:31:12,850 --> 00:31:13,260
Well,

471
00:31:15,330 --> 00:31:17,170
