472
00:31:18,940 --> 00:31:21,500
I will now return to the palace
to report.

473
00:31:25,570 --> 00:31:27,700
Chagu, I'll meet my brother soon.

474
00:31:29,460 --> 00:31:30,700
Great Yan places great importance
on etiquette.

475
00:31:30,780 --> 00:31:32,090
There are many dignitaries in Zhaojing.

476
00:31:32,220 --> 00:31:34,170
We must be even more cautious
in our actions from now on.

477
00:31:34,170 --> 00:31:35,220
After we become dignitaries
through marriage alliance,

478
00:31:35,220 --> 00:31:36,370
no one will dare to bully us.

479
00:31:36,370 --> 00:31:37,980
I heard there was no Crown Princess
in the Eastern Palace.

480
00:31:38,220 --> 00:31:39,610
The Crown Prince doesn't fancy
just any woman.

481
00:31:39,700 --> 00:31:41,220
Ssh, stop talking.

482
00:32:07,410 --> 00:32:08,220
Your Highness,

483
00:32:08,220 --> 00:32:09,020
His Majesty has given an order

484
00:32:09,020 --> 00:32:10,980
prohibiting Your Highness from paying
respects to Empress Dejia.

