have come back alive.

491
00:34:39,300 --> 00:34:43,500
[Memorial to Empress Dejia of Great Yan]

492
00:34:56,060 --> 00:34:56,980
Rebel!

493
00:34:57,210 --> 00:34:58,650
How dare you wear a wedding gown?

494
00:35:00,540 --> 00:35:01,340
Jinghe,

495
00:35:02,020 --> 00:35:03,130
today is the day of Mother's burial.

496
00:35:03,650 --> 00:35:05,020
How can you wear a wedding gown?

497
00:35:06,860 --> 00:35:08,340
What's there to celebrate?

498
00:35:10,290 --> 00:35:11,020
Jinghe,

499
00:35:11,460 --> 00:35:12,770
you scoundrel!

500
00:35:14,210 --> 00:35:15,420
Great Yan reclaiming Qingzhou

501
00:35:16,020 --> 00:35:17,500
was not for the sake
of reclaiming an empty city.

502
00:35:19,340 --> 00:35:20,380
You show no remorse

503
00:35:20,380 --> 00:35:21,250
and are disobedient and disrespectful.

504
00:35:21,820 --> 00:35:22,860
You are unworthy to pay respects
to the Empress.

505
00:35:23,210 --> 00:35:23,770
Drag him out.

506
00:36:02,700 --> 00:36:06,100
