511
00:36:22,020 --> 00:36:22,610
Speak.

512
00:36:23,170 --> 00:36:24,610
Who sent you here?

513
00:36:25,250 --> 00:36:26,290
I'll tell you.

514
00:36:27,170 --> 00:36:28,770
I am a guard
at the West Suburbs Barracks.

515
00:36:28,980 --> 00:36:31,730
