the people to kill the mass murderer.

516
00:36:31,980 --> 00:36:33,540
Your superiors are mass murderers.

517
00:36:34,770 --> 00:36:35,820
It's been ten years,

518
00:36:36,340 --> 00:36:39,250
and you're still using the same means
to harm Prince Jing.

519
00:37:16,420 --> 00:37:18,620
[Weibei]

520
00:37:20,290 --> 00:37:20,860
My lord,

521
00:37:21,380 --> 00:37:22,130
it's been arranged.

522
00:37:23,060 --> 00:37:25,020
We've asked Lianxiu to take
the wedding gown to the Buddhist Hall.

523
00:37:36,130 --> 00:37:37,500
Before you left for Qingzhou,

524
00:37:37,690 --> 00:37:39,570
you promised the Empress
that upon your return,

525
00:37:39,570 --> 00:37:41,250
you would lay down your armor
and change into wedding attire.

526
00:37:42,130 --> 00:37:43,290
The Empress
had been looking forward to it.

527
00:37:44,820 --> 00:37:47,500
Upon hearing that you would return
after winning a great victory,

528
00:37:48,060 --> 00:37:50,210
the Empress sought an auspicious day
for completing the needlework,

529
00:37:52,500 --> 00:37:53,290
but it ended up

530
00:37:54,540 --> 00:37:56,340
being the day of Her Majesty's funeral.

531
00:37:59,250 --> 00:38:01,290
