To fulfill your promise to the Empress,

532
00:38:02,090 --> 00:38:04,650
you wore wedding attire
on the day of the funeral.

533
00:38:06,090 --> 00:38:07,820
Why didn't you explain it,

534
00:38:08,860 --> 00:38:10,980
