what he wishes to.

537
00:38:22,940 --> 00:38:23,940
So did my mother.

538
00:38:29,980 --> 00:38:31,090
You may leave.

539
00:38:31,820 --> 00:38:33,420
I want to be alone.

540
00:38:44,250 --> 00:38:45,020
Mother,

541
00:38:46,170 --> 00:38:47,460
your son, the mass murderer,

542
00:38:49,170 --> 00:38:50,020
is back.

543
00:38:52,210 --> 00:38:53,290
I guess you didn't expect it.

544
00:38:55,170 --> 00:38:56,250
The mass murderer

545
00:38:57,340 --> 00:38:58,980
could come back.

546
00:39:00,570 --> 00:39:02,770
Do not point blades at the people.

547
00:39:03,730 --> 00:39:06,090
These were your teachings, Mother.

548
00:39:06,500 --> 00:39:07,770
But why,

549
00:39:08,570 --> 00:39:10,570
